    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The following code will result in an infinite loop in Zend_Date constructor.</p>

&lt;?php
  $date_xml = "00-11130000000";
  $date_obj = new Zend_Date( $date_xml, "yyyyMMddHHmmss" );
  echo $date_obj-&gt;toString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss");
?&gt;

